features: 3 Tier Monitor Stand: This 3-tier monitor stand riser is ideal for saving space and keeping your computer monitor, keyboard, laptop, scanner, printer and other office supplies neat and organized

Large Storage Capacity: 3 open shelves of different sizes provide ample storage space for your books, files, notebooks, stationery, cables, headphones, camera, etc. A built-in charging station with 2 USB ports keeps your electronic devices full-charged and organized

Sturdy & Stable: This printer stand is made of thick partialboard and strong metal frame, ensuring its stability and durability. The maximum load capacity of each shelf is 44 lbs. Anti-slip pads at the bottom of the legs prevent the stand from scratching the floor and keep it stable

Space-Saving Design: This computer stand has a compact size of 11.81" D x 15.75" W x 24.41" H, which fits perfectly in your home office, dorm, living room, bedroom and other places. It provides extra space for your work and life

Easy to Assemble: Detailed instructions and all necessary hardware are included. This printer stand is easy to assemble. Please feel free to contact us if you have any questions about our computer stand
body.description: This VEDECASA 3-tier printer stand is not only a printer stand but also a storage organizer. It is perfect for placing in your home office, living room, dorm, or bedroom to store and organize your printer, scanner, fax machine, office supplies, and documents. The printer stand has 3 storage drawers and an open shelf, which can meet your different storage needs. The top drawer can hold up to 22 lbs, and each shelf can hold up to 11 lbs. The charging station design is perfect for placing your cell phone, tablet, watch, headphones, and other electronics, which can make your daily charging more convenient. This printer stand is made of high-quality MDF and metal, which is sturdy and durable. The surface is smooth and easy to clean with a damp cloth. The dimensions of the printer stand are 11.81" D x 15.75" W x 24.41" H.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars HP 4-IN-1 PRINTER HANGS OVER EDGES OF STAND
reviews.reviewText: This attractive printer stand looks great in and of itself, and wherever it is used. Pretty much everything about this stand is wonderful. Not only does the stand have an aesthetically pleasing appearance, but it is also well-made and quite sturdy. The printer stand has an all-metal frame, 3 sturdy wood veneer shelves, and a roomy (collapsible) fabric drawer that can be positioned anywhere on the stand. You can configure and rearrange the middle 2 shelves and the drawer to your liking, making this printer stand quite versatile. The charging station has 2 receptacles and 2 USB ports. The charging station is powered by an attached cord that plugs into a wall receptacle (outlet). This printer stand was easy to assemble (tools provided).Besides being used as a printer stand, this stand also would work well as an end table or as a nightstand.This printer stand is sized a bit small to adequately accommodate a HP ENVY Inspire all-in-one printer. A printer of this size will hang over all 4 edges of this printer stand.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This printer stand is easily strong enough to hold one printer or even two printers
reviews.reviewText: It took about an hour to assemble but went together with no problems. Everything fit together perfectly. Someone said that it was not strong enough to hold a standard printer, well I have a Canon printer on the top and an Epson photo printer on the middle shelf with a thick ream of paper in the drawer at the bottom. I don't recommend that you sit or stand on it but this is not a weak or wobbly printer stand. The casters roll around easily and I can move the printers without having to pick them up and make my back hurt. I'm very happy with this printer stand. Oh, it looks nice too.
